#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Spilleregler"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You have to find balls hidden in the black box. Your means are limited - "
#| "you can just fire lasers which are around the box. There are three "
#| "possible outcomes for each ray you send into the box:"
msgid ""
"You have to find balls hidden in the black box. Your means are limited - you "
"can just fire lasers which are around the box. There are three possible "
"outcomes for each beam you send into the box:"
msgstr ""
"Du skal finde boldene gemt i den sorte kasse. Dine metoder er begrænsede - "
"du kan blot affyre lasere som er omkring kassen. Der er tre mulige "
"resultater for hver stråle du sender ind i feltet:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detour"
msgstr "Detour"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The ray is deflected and emerges somewhere other than where you sent it "
#| "in. On the playfield, detours are denoted by matching pairs of numbers - "
#| "one where the ray went in, and the other where it came out."
msgid ""
"The beam is deflected and emerges somewhere other than where you sent it in. "
"On the playfield, detours are denoted by matching pairs of numbers - one "
"where the beam went in, and the other where it came out."
msgstr ""
"Strålen afbøjes og kommer ud et andet sted end der hvor du sendte den ind. "
"På spillefeltet vises dette med et par tal - et hvor strålen gik ind, og et "
"hvor den kom ud."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reflection"
msgstr "Refleksion"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The ray is reflected and emerges in the same place it was sent in. On the "
#| "playfield, reflections are denoted by the letter <guilabel>R</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"The beam is reflected and emerges in the same place it was sent in. On the "
"playfield, reflections are denoted by a special sign."
msgstr ""
"Strålen reflekteres og kommer ud samme sted som der hvor den kom ind. På "
"spillefeltet er refleksioner vist med bogstavet <guilabel>R</guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Hit</term>"
msgstr "<term>Træf</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The ray strikes a ball directly and is absorbed. It does not emerge from "
#| "the box. On the playfield, hits are denoted by the letter <guilabel>H</"
#| "guilabel>."
msgid ""
"The beam strikes a ball and is absorbed. It does not emerge from the box. On "
"the playfield, hits are denoted by a special sign."
msgstr ""
"Strålen rammer en bold og absorberes. Den kommer ikke ud af feltet igen. På "
"spillefeltet vises dette med bogstavet <guilabel>H</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The rules for how balls deflect rays are simple and are best shown by "
#| "example."
msgid ""
"The rules for how balls deflect beams are simple and are best shown by "
"example."
msgstr ""
"Reglerne for hvordan en stråle afbøjes er simple og bedst vist ved et "
"eksempel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As a ray approaches a ball it is deflected ninety degrees. Rays can be "
#| "deflected multiple times. In the diagrams below, the dashes represent "
#| "empty box locations and the letter <guilabel>O</guilabel> represents a "
#| "ball. The entrance and exit points of each ray are marked with numbers as "
#| "described under <link linkend=\"detour\">Detour</link> above. Note that "
#| "the entrance and exit points are always interchangeable. <guilabel>*</"
#| "guilabel> denotes the path taken by the ray."
msgid ""
"As a beam approaches a ball it is deflected ninety degrees. Beams can be "
"deflected multiple times. In the diagrams below, the dashes represent empty "
"box locations and the letter <guilabel>O</guilabel> represents a ball. The "
"entrance and exit points of each beam are marked with numbers as described "
"under <link linkend=\"detour\">Detour</link> above. Note that the entrance "
"and exit points are always interchangeable. <guilabel>*</guilabel> denotes "
"the path taken by the beam."
msgstr ""
"Når en stråle nærmer sig en bold afbøjes den halvfems grader. Stråler kan "
"afbøjes flere gange. I diagrammerne nedenfor, repræsenterer tomme kasser og "
"bogstavet <guilabel>O</guilabel> bolde. Indgang og udgang af hver stråle er "
"markerede med tal som vist under <link linkend=\"detour\">Detour</link> "
"ovenfor. Bemærk at indgangspunkt og udgangspunkt altid kan byttes om. "
"<guilabel>*</guilabel> viser den sti strålen tager."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note carefully the relative positions of the ball and the ninety degree "
"deflection it causes."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk omhyggeligt de relative positioner af bolden og den 90 graders "
"afbøjning det forårsager."

